{"title":"Trazodona Riesgo CV","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Trazodona Riesgo CV iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Trazodona y\\NRiesgo\\NCardiovascular","guid":"HAoFI20FmfcPDUodDj2Ryg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología\\NBásica","guid":"fONEPr7IjH7cF0Ohapl5mA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Clase: SARI (Serotonin Antagonist and Reuptake Inhibitor)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Mecanismo principal → antagonismo 5-HT2A + inhibición recaptación 5-HT","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Antagonismo alfa-1 adrenérgico → RESPONSABLE de efectos CV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Bloqueo H1 histaminérgico → sedación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Mínima actividad anticolinérgica (ventaja vs TCA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Metabolismo hepático CYP3A4 → inhibidores aumentan niveles","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Vida media 5-9h (liberación inmediata) / ~10h (liberación prolongada)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Dosis antidepresiva: 150-300 mg/día","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Dosis hipnótica (off-label): 25-100 mg/noche","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Efectos\\NCardiovasculares\\NDirectos","guid":"R39H_3wdCK7TvVyaMLxi7w","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Hipotensión\\Nortostática","guid":"riD80E5t3WygfW5qvaaRTA","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Por bloqueo alfa-1 adrenérgico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"MAYOR riesgo en AM y cardiópatas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"Dosis-dependiente → titular lento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"Riesgo de caídas y fracturas en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"12","text":"Puede causar síncope","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"11","text":"Prolongación\\Ndel intervalo\\NQTc","guid":"vq8kEPQru5B4ONgdS0ezsg","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Mecanismo: bloqueo canales hERG (Ikr)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"Incidencia baja pero CLÍNICAMENTE SIGNIFICATIVA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"Riesgo aumenta con: dosis altas, inhibidores CYP3A4, hipokalemia, hipomagnesemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"Puede desencadenar Torsade de Pointes (TdP)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"Monitorizar ECG basal y post-inicio en pacientes de riesgo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"11","text":"Arritmias\\Ncardíacas","guid":"ZUJBdzGegukHNQJj7vlndg","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Reportes de arritmias ventriculares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Bradicardia en algunos casos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Fibrilación auricular (reportes aislados)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"24","text":"Riesgo mayor con sobredosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"11","text":"Frecuencia\\Ncardíaca","guid":"01tLCfMFndENFnNp7PHpUg","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Puede causar bradicardia leve","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"Diferencia vs ISRS que tienden a aumentar FC","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Contraindicaciones\\Ny Precauciones en\\NContexto Agudo","guid":"u4bFErlmDQMA9ntYfHZ4qA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"INFARTO AGUDO DE\\NMIOCARDIO (IAM)\\NRECIENTE","guid":"MQR0A8C5AXfzpjeHyVXRvw","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"NO recomendado en fase aguda (<2 semanas post-IAM)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Hipotensión ortostática → compromiso perfusión coronaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Prolongación QTc → riesgo arritmias en miocardio isquémico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"Miocardio vulnerable a arritmias ventriculares post-IAM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"Si depresión post-IAM → ISRS primera línea (sertralina)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"33","text":"SADHART: sertralina segura desde 2 semanas post-IAM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"33","text":"ENRICHD: confirmó seguridad de ISRS en post-IAM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"32","text":"Síndrome Coronario\\NAgudo (SCA)","guid":"RZioAi3eB5kLL8-qa3ndjQ","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Evitar en fase aguda por inestabilidad hemodinámica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Hipotensión puede empeorar isquemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Interacción con antiplaquetarios (menor vs ISRS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"Valorar riesgo-beneficio solo post-estabilización","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"32","text":"Insuficiencia\\NCardíaca\\NDescompensada","guid":"zlUoXtiJtDO0QsVnI0UJDw","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Precaución extrema → hipotensión empeora bajo gasto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"ISRS preferibles (sertralina, escitalopram)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Si ya en uso → monitorizar PA y FC estrechamente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"32","text":"Arritmias\\NVentriculares\\NActivas","guid":"c-_1kQn4aAQeSgEVql6Nag","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"CONTRAINDICADA si QTc >500ms","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"No usar con otros fármacos que prolongan QTc","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"Bupropión: menor riesgo de prolongación QTc","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"32","text":"Bloqueo AV de Alto Grado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Precaución por efectos sobre conducción","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"0","text":"Interacciones\\NCV Relevantes","guid":"Te1KhyC_tM21O0nxENdy5w","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Inhibidores CYP3A4 →\\Naumentan niveles de\\Ntrazodona","guid":"d3DSPLgxPHpj2UFFSdA58g","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Ketoconazol, itraconazol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Ritonavir y otros antiretrovirales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Claritromicina, eritromicina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"Diltiazem, verapamilo → ATENCION en cardiópatas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"Jugo de pomelo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"56","text":"Otros prolongadores\\Nde QTc","guid":"JLZvaXkcXtQ698IgFitP_A","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Amiodarona → EVITAR combinación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"Sotalol, dronedarona","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"Haloperidol → riesgo aditivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"63","text":"Ondansetrón a dosis altas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"63","text":"Fluoroquinolonas (moxifloxacino)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"56","text":"Antihipertensivos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Efecto aditivo hipotensor con IECA, ARA-II, BB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"Mayor riesgo en AM polimedicados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"Ajustar dosis antihipertensiva si inicia trazodona","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"56","text":"Anticoagulantes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Mínima interacción con warfarina (ventaja vs ISRS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"ISRS tienen mayor riesgo de sangrado por efecto antiplaquetario","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"Evidencia en IAM y\\NRiesgo Cardiovascular","guid":"VjSqPFN0qsvKTzcp_CYhaA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Estudio caso-control\\N(Alqdwah-Fattouh 2020,\\NBr J Clin Pharmacol)","guid":"A5wArCWMDPhQ5dFbmEYZxQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"n=24155 casos IAM vs 120775 controles","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"Trazodona REDUJO riesgo de IAM (OR 0.76, IC95% 0.64-0.91)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"ISRS también protectores (OR 0.86, IC95% 0.81-0.93)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"Efecto duración-dependiente sugerido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"77","text":"Posible mecanismo: antagonismo 5-HT2A antiplaquetario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"76","text":"Revisión Teply 2016\\N(Prog Cardiovasc Dis)","guid":"WWDiQB9ESsuXzl7ZBEvN-A","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Trazodona asociada a hipotensión ortostática y riesgo de arritmias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"En cardiopatía isquémica → sertralina primera elección","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"ISRS y IRSN relativamente seguros en IC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"TCA y MAOI EVITAR en cardiópatas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"76","text":"Fagiolini 2023\\N(Ann Gen\\NPsychiatry)","guid":"LXby8BE2RDaB4-MiXyB9tQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Trazodona: baja incidencia de hipotensión ortostática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"Especial precaución en AM y cardiópatas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"Prolongación QTc y arritmias infrecuentes pero posibles","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"88","text":"Formulación liberación prolongada puede mejorar tolerabilidad","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"0","text":"Manejo Práctico en\\NPaciente Geriátrico\\NCardiópata","guid":"3y8Vj9dP2E1zmRaMgxzijA","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"ANTES de\\Nprescribir","guid":"0QHB9PyLNgCDImjkKvXXig","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"ECG basal (QTc)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"Electrolitos (K+, Mg2+)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"94","text":"Lista completa de fármacos → revisar interacciones QTc","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"94","text":"Presión arterial de pie y acostado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"94","text":"Función renal y hepática","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"93","text":"Dosificación\\Ngeriátrica","guid":"8oCcXtoGmCoaAM7ze0RZVg","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Inicio: 25 mg noche (mitad de dosis estándar)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"Titulación lenta: aumentar 25 mg cada 1-2 semanas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"Dosis máxima sugerida en AM: 150 mg/día","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"Start low, go slow, but dont go nowhere","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"93","text":"Monitorización","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"PA ortostática semanal primeras 2-4 semanas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"ECG control a las 2 semanas o con cambio de dosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Vigilar mareos, síncope, caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"Reevaluar indicación cada 3-6 meses","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"93","text":"Cuándo NO usar trazodona\\N(elegir alternativa)","guid":"t4SFqB8d9w4zfel7mrhoKQ","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"IAM reciente (<4-6 semanas) → sertralina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"QTc basal >450 ms → bupropión o mirtazapina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"Hipotensión ortostática sintomática → bupropión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"Uso de amiodarona u otro prolongador QTc → bupropión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"110","text":"IC con FEVI <35% → sertralina","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"Alternativas en Paciente\\NPost-IAM con Depresión","guid":"4oKnhANicl95Kf7PL6P7Ow","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Primera línea: Sertralina (SADHART)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Segura desde 2 semanas post-IAM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"Sin efecto significativo sobre QTc","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"Actividad antiplaquetaria adicional","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"116","text":"Segunda línea: Escitalopram","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Buena evidencia en IC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"Menor interacción farmacológica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"116","text":"Tercera línea: Mirtazapina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"Sin prolongación QTc significativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"Riesgo: aumento de peso, sedación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"116","text":"Considerar: Bupropión","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Menor riesgo QTc de todos los AD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Evitar en epilepsia y TCA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"Útil si predomina apatía/fatiga","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"116","text":"TCC (Terapia Cognitivo-Conductual)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Evidencia en post-IAM (estudio ENRICHD)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Sin riesgos CV","guid":"","children":[]},